show.description: ​On August 9, 2024, a 31-year-old female postgraduate trainee doctor at Kolkata's R.G. Kar Medical College and Hospital was found raped and murdered on campus. The prime accused, Sanjay Roy, a civic volunteer, was convicted and sentenced to life imprisonment in January 2025.
show.description_secondary: ​On August 9, 2024, a 31-year-old female postgraduate trainee doctor at Kolkata's R.G. Kar Medical College and Hospital was found raped and murdered on campus.
